/*       Last Amend No. CUP042 *REDUNDANT  Date 12Dec14              */
/* Bank Fusion Midas 1.4 Base ---------------------------------------*/
/* Midas Plus 1.4 Base 04 -------------------------------------------*/
/* Midas Plus 1.4 Base ----------------------------------------------*/
